argest scales into thermal energy and microscale fluctuations, without the\nneed for a scale-by-scale turbulent cascade.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 May 2017 18:01:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 May 2017 13:17:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 Dec 2017 16:56:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-14"}
